WorkItem.Description:
When defining a getter or setter, the resulting compiled JavaScript code fails at the following:

 Object.defineProperty(XmlElement.prototype, "TagName", {

For some reason, defineProperty is undefined.   I tried searching if this is a known issue already.

Edit:
Forgot to include that this is an issue in IE10.

Re-edit:
Please close issue, for some reason the browser was in IE7-standards mode and I didn't notice it.

Comments.Message: It is the problem of our esteemed and dear IE browser.
